{"tid":197151,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［迷途迷途孤兒］第一次買平機票飛美帝","createTime":"2017-04-11T17:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T09:40:23.000Z","uid":85765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23d72a133ac80e3a5e7acd2f5e191584bf2aae41","tid":197151,"uid":85765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"打算買機票去Richmond 但對過時間同價錢 決定坐AA （貴價訓不如平價訓 坐成25個鐘）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由凌晨香港出發：<br />\n第一班機飛到東京(CX) 4個半鐘gap <br />\n第二班機飛到達拉斯(AA) 2個半鐘 gap<br />\n第三班先去到Richmond(AA) 下午到步<br />\n<br />\n然後我有2個疑問麻煩各位解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. 每次轉機小弟都要拎番行李再check in過？<br />\n<br />\n2. 都預左會有delay既情況 第一次轉有4個幾鐘我都安心d 但第二次得2個半鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有無過來人可以講下係唔係咁少時間好易出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁多先 麻煩各短幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc90b5badb42a5629c6adeb6ff51b70b584bb10d","tid":197151,"uid":43964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"2.5鐘一啲都唔少.....去馬啦，到左美國行李要再過機！"},{"pid":"daeff3ba877ac8a96ca7dfce72bce1ead1bcf3f7","tid":197151,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:26:36.000Z","msg":"點解唔坐UA"},{"pid":"5b65a14a88d08b06dfb79d48b1c31cc302d99381","tid":197151,"uid":85765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:36:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔坐UA</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貴d AA 5000有 同埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重坐UA?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f90fd66a2a4ce253888a1dfe1ba13f08cebf289","tid":197151,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔坐UA</block